comments.body:
> Add a base_branch input to agent-implement.yml for both workflow_dispatch and workflow_call, defaulting to "".

Clarifying question before coding: should base_branch be accepted only as a branch name, or should it also accept PR numbers like base_pr: 123 and resolve that PR’s head branch automatically? My recommendation for the first PR is branch-name only, then add PR-number resolution once the basic stacked PR path is proven.

@sepo-agent /answer I think it's very minimum cost to support both cases right? I think the only thing is to make sure the we define / reuse a proper format for the "base_pr: 123" and then supporting both should be simple enough?
